    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is flawless! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks just as stunning as the day I bought it\u2014seriously, not a single blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and feels brand new. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
