      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3, a definitive example of the E46 chassis. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is mated to a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been serviced preventatively, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The suspension maintains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these cars are known for. With flawless paint depth and a cockpit devoid of typical bolster wear, this is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
