    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained to an exacting standard that rivals its original showroom floor condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin is flawless, with supple leather seats showing zero signs of wear and all technology operating perfectly. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, and a complete binder of documentation accompanies the sale. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically perfect, cosmetically pristine example that has been pampered since day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
