    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing no signs of wear, this unit represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin environment, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare. This is an uncompromising choice for the discerning driver seeking a vehicle of peerless quality and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 43500.0,
