    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road today. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
