    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is equipped with the ZCP Competition Package, providing a 10mm lower ride height and specifically tuned Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and Dynamic Stability Control (DSC) mapping. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively. The Alpine White exterior is free of imperfections, and the carbon fiber roof remains structurally pristine with no clear coat degradation. The interior features Novillo leather with zero bolster wear, reflecting its pampered history. A turn-key, mechanically superlative example for the serious driver.",
